    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_6_695-711",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "695-711",
      "markText": "身濒危而志愈壮，道处困而造弥深。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=711",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=695&rangeEnd=711"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_4391-4422",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "4391-4422",
      "markText": "身之主宰便是心，心之所发便是意，意之本体便是知，意之所在便是物",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_5_1473-1500",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1473-1500",
      "markText": "凡读书者以身践之，则书与我为一；以言视之，则判然二耳。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1473&rangeEnd=1500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1473&rangeEnd=1500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_3_554-580",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "554-580",
      "markText": "阳明先生被后人誉为“立德、立言、立功”三不朽的完人。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=580"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_2188-2245",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2188-2245",
      "markText": "《礼记》言：‘孝子之有深爱者，必有和气；有和气者，必有愉色；有愉色者，必有婉容。’须是有个深爱做根，便自然如此。”",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2188&rangeEnd=2245",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2188&rangeEnd=2245"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_1796-1882",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1796-1882",
      "markText": "都只在此心。心即理也。此心无私欲之蔽，即是天理，不须外面添一分。以此纯乎天理之心，发之事父便是孝，发之事君便是忠，发之交友治民便是信与仁。只在此心去人欲、存天理上用功便是。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1882",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1882"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_5435-5460",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "5435-5460",
      "markText": "天理、人欲不并立，安有天理为主，人欲又从而听命者？",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5435&rangeEnd=5460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5435&rangeEnd=5460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_10650-10674",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "10650-10674",
      "markText": "持志如心痛。一心在痛上，岂有工夫说闲话、管闲事。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10650&rangeEnd=10674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10650&rangeEnd=10674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_11946-12040",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "11946-12040",
      "markText": "立志用功，如种树然。方其根芽，犹未有干；及其有干，尚未有枝；枝而后叶，叶而后花实。初种根时，只管栽培灌溉，勿作枝想，勿作叶想，勿作花想，勿作实想。悬想何益！但不忘栽培之功，怕没有枝叶花实？",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=11946&rangeEnd=12040",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=11946&rangeEnd=12040"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_3_1218-1294",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1218-1294",
      "markText": "如原文中的“折衷”，国家标准中的推荐词形是“折中”，则统一改成“折中”。再如原文中的“甚么”，推荐词形是“什么”，因国家标准未作规定，所以依旧保持原样。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1294",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1294"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_12_591-645",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "591-645",
      "markText": "圣贤教人如医用药，皆因病立方，酌其虚实温凉阴阳内外而时时加减之，要在去病，初无定说。若拘执一方，鲜不杀人矣。",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_1654-1674",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1654-1674",
      "markText": "心即理也。天下又有心外之事，心外之理乎？",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1654&rangeEnd=1674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1654&rangeEnd=1674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_10306-10332",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "10306-10332",
      "markText": "人须在事上磨，方能立得住，方能‘静亦定，动亦定’。”",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10306&rangeEnd=10332",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10306&rangeEnd=10332"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_16738-16769",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "16738-16769",
      "markText": "“喜怒哀乐本体自是中和的。才自家着些意思，便过不及，便是私。”",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=16738&rangeEnd=16769",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=16738&rangeEnd=16769"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_31665-31679",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "31665-31679",
      "markText": "已与汝一句道尽，汝尚自不会。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=31665&rangeEnd=31679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=31665&rangeEnd=31679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_3_599-630",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "599-630",
      "markText": "阳明学不仅是中国儒学五百年来的源头活水，其影响力更是远播日韩。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=599&rangeEnd=630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=599&rangeEnd=630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_26583-26612",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "26583-26612",
      "markText": "悔悟是去病之药，然以改之为贵。若留滞于中，则又因药发病。”",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=26583&rangeEnd=26612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=26583&rangeEnd=26612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_13_1109-1155",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1109-1155",
      "markText": "其后剖析愈精，考拟愈繁，著述愈富，而支离愈甚，间有觉其非而欲挽焉，则又未能尽追窠臼而洗濯之。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1109&rangeEnd=1155",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1109&rangeEnd=1155"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "857258_18_6617-6709",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "6617-6709",
      "markText": "天下所以不治，只因文盛实衰，人出己见，新奇相高，以眩俗取誉，徒以乱天下之聪明，涂天下之耳目，使天下靡然争务修饰文词，以求知于世，而不复知有敦本尚实、反朴还淳之行，是皆著述者有以启之。”",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=857258&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=6617&rangeEnd=6709",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f2632e705d14aaf2659ee88?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=6617&rangeEnd=6709"
    }
